Notebook[{
Cell["InfraSegment", "Title",ExpressionUUID->"453bc3f4-b7d8-44f3-9a35-02ac9610d897"],

Cell["[LLM Generated]", "Subtitle",ExpressionUUID->"52184377-4da1-4076-82ca-4753f17d6947"],

Cell["\<\
InfraSegment is the wrapper head for path realisations of the segment / line \
/ parallel / common-line primitives. InfraSegment[{path}] is the unary form; \
InfraSegment[{path1, \[Ellipsis], pathk}] is the multi-realisation form. \
FindInfraSegment, FindInfraLine, ExtendInfraSegment, FindInfraParallel, and FindInfraCommonLine all \
emit a List of unary InfraSegment[{path}] wrappers. Wrapping that List with \
InfraSegment @ \[Ellipsis] collapses it to the multi form via auto-flatten; \
InfraSceneHighlight consumes the multi form with sequential-edge semantics.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"618f3eaf-bf84-44b0-95a0-9a146d47bfc3"],

Cell["Setup", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"6f6d1f25-7028-42eb-8458-7fd4a26aebd0"],

